{"tid":300142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來新移民家庭既來港速度，仲擴散得快過癌細胞","createTime":"2017-06-27T15:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T01:43:30.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d5ac3ae67fe8a4c41b53fe7f1986ce6ad7daca4","tid":300142,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T15:48:53.000Z","msg":"今日聽我媽話，當初我呀姨黎到香港<br />\n係因為佢奶奶係香港人<br />\n跟住佢奶奶申請我姨丈落黎<br />\n我姨丈再申請我呀姨同佢兩個仔落黎<br />\n兩個仔分別再申請埋佢地既老婆仔女落黎<br />\n一個生兩個，一個生三個<br />\n落到黎喊苦喊忽無屋住，事實係內地住過千呎既屋<br />\n又話凑住小朋友，做唔到野要攞綜緩<br />\n講到呢度，一個老人家巳申請到十一個人<br />\n三個家庭落黎<br />\n但係未完，重點係，我姨個奶奶係有三仔一女（呢度粗略估計又幾十人）<br />\n仲有，原來過關時，會有人幫呢D新移民家庭架，不過就唔知係社會福利署定係一D民間組織<br />\n真係攞命呀<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.baby-kingdom.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=19976849\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.baby-kingdom.com%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D19976849&d=uqiiUrotIIEMmpeAN6H3AY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=29525e4b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.baby-kingdom.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=19976849</a>"},{"pid":"0adb26014f5ac93b4fc13e174aa7f0b63436e32d","tid":300142,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T15:51:18.000Z","msg":"連登仔只著眼蝻"},{"pid":"041530fa6fd4908503ebe002b98a5db76b7a6c74","tid":300142,"uid":91931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T15:53:45.000Z","msg":"同舊時個D比慢唔知幾撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係牛屎佬幾倍數量"},{"pid":"f25047f13895b7a1fda5e5f8bc0b4522bcaf2b73","tid":300142,"uid":1069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T16:05:49.000Z","msg":"仲有假結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 十萬一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ecb3ac0dc076a7baa37e8dc0391d8fb292b24a7","tid":300142,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T00:44:38.000Z","msg":"根本好多落來養老，近年都無用『人口新力軍』打飛機"},{"pi